Package subsetsum

Class Sublist

  • java.lang.Object
    • subsetsum.Sublist
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class Sublist
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    The class Sublist stores a reference to the master list from which we are forming a sublist and also stores the indices and the sum of the objects. The class uses an ArrayList<> of integers which are indices of each elements in the master set to represent the actual sublist that is derived from the master set
